name: L'ami Gourmet

featured_reviews.review_id:
Coffee shop / fast food recemment reouvert apres reamenagement.
Le cadre est agreable, la decoration est moderne et attirante, dispose d'une terrasse avec ventilateurs nebuliseurs, a l'interieur on trouve un coin cafe, et un espace familial.
La carte proposee presente un menu sale, mais on peut prendre des desserts, des glaces et diverses boissons sont proposees.
On a pris des glaces et c'etait tres bon, mais les patisseries sont moins bonnes. Les pizzas avaient l'air delicieuses, a essayer !
On y est bien accueilli et servi, et les prix sont dans la moyenne.
Dispose de deux grands parkings (le meme que le supermarche a cote)
Nous reviendrons, je recommande !

featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
Coffee shop / fast food recently re-opened after refurbishment.
The setting is pleasant, the decoration is modern and attractive, has a terrace with nebulizer fans, inside there is a coffee corner, and a family area.
The menu offered has a savory menu, but you can have desserts, ice creams and various drinks are available.
We had ice cream and it was very good, but the pastries are less good. The pizzas looked delicious, give it a try!
We are well received and served, and the prices are average.
Has two large car parks (the same as the supermarket next door)
We will be back, I recommend!
